        "message": "LU-0000 tests: Verify setupall correctly fails\n\n******* Test patch for: *******\n\nsetupall function under test-framework never fails.\nEven if the mount from mount[mgs/oss] or start()\ncall is a faiure. Somewhere within a chain of calls\nfrom setupall() to do_nodes() the return value is\ngetting lost and 0 is always returning.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity\nSigned-off-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nChange-Id: I6aca804806e6daae46934212e385bbfedc912ec6\n"
